				{Username: "user1", YesSharesOwned: 2, NoSharesOwned: 0},
			},
		},
	}
	for _, tc := range testcases {
		t.Run(tc.Name, func(t *testing.T) {
			actual := NetAggregateMarketPositions(tc.AggregatedPositions)
